{"tid":1090704,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唔開心嘅人不妨入嚟睇下，我提供幾個方法令大家開心啲。","createTime":"2019-04-03T16:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T08:59:25.000Z","uid":227650,"like":90,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6ff48f6c1a6fbeb6e37420b8934be9849be27988","tid":1090704,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:03:12.000Z","msg":"1.做運動<br />\n<br />\n2.搵朋友傾計<br />\n<br />\n以上呢兩個方法應該好多人知同埋算係幾大路， 跟住我會提供兩個比較冷門啲/冇咁多人講過嘅方法。<br />\n<br />\n3.飲奶茶或者咖啡:<span style=\"color: red;\">奶茶或咖啡有刺激大腦釋放令人興奮的多巴胺，而且咖啡因會令身體處於亢奮狀態。</span> 但始終唔健康，所以唔建議大家成日飲。<br />\n<br />\n4.諗你期待嘅事:<span style=\"color: red;\">只要係期待嘅事就得，就算有少少天荒夜談</span><br />\n<br />\n以上四個方法我自己都試過，絕對係work嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望幫到唔開心嘅人啦。"},{"pid":"572b94ee1416f3cfec9545fd8886601ad54de085","tid":1090704,"uid":227650,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:05:15.000Z","msg":"頭先喺感情台開過，唔多人覆;唯有喺度開多次"},{"pid":"08118ab780be7fcb26e69a680aa691cb20a51cd5","tid":1090704,"uid":48631,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:06:41.000Z","msg":"飲完咖啡半粒鐘之內一家要all尿,係咪正常?"},{"pid":"91b7fddb92b5025e269938870a3d16d1d3c7b719","tid":1090704,"uid":20449,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:07:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d624a0b86a501ce9f2a39166c48da6685ff56130","tid":1090704,"uid":227650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"08118ab780be7fcb26e69a680aa691cb20a51cd5","tid":1090704,"uid":48631,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:06:41.000Z","msg":"飲完咖啡半粒鐘之內一家要all尿,係咪正常?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:10:52.000Z","msg":"正常"},{"pid":"8cf6c74112236242801fb2e6ff70c551ae5f8bd1","tid":1090704,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:18:28.000Z","msg":"冇朋友可以講"},{"pid":"01a601a3ecff93b249d06b945c892668b5ca80c2","tid":1090704,"uid":227650,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pi